,"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The text of 46 App. U.S.C. 1295f(d) is omitted because it apparently was intended to apply to former 46 App. U.S.C. 1295f(c), which was repealed in 1983.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
